@*
    Default.cshtml
    FreshHarvestMarket

    This view renders the Weather ViewComponent output,
    displaying current weather information for the marketplace.

    It shows:
    - Current temperature (in Fahrenheit)
    - A contextual weather message based on conditions
    - A simple, centered UI display for use in layouts or pages

    This component helps inform users about weather conditions
    that may affect their pickup experience at Fresh Harvest Market.
*@

<div class="text-center">
    <p class="mb-0">
        🌡️ @ViewBag.Temp°F — @ViewBag.Message
    </p>
</div>